Living rm is lg and bright, features wood insert firelplace w/lg stone hearth. Exterior paint 2018. Enclosed sunroom w/ wood stove;bank of windows to appreciate beautiful views and ext access. Attached oversized carport. Garage/shop is oversized has newer door, AND offers access to vehicle under carraige from lower above grade level! washer/dryer hutch dining table available at no extra cost. If you are looking for a larger parcel, move in ready home, rural and private without being remote THIS IS IT! Vacation home? Airbnb? Your country place?
